name: Rogue-dungen
body:
### Welcome to the Rogue DunGen Website!
This is a python library that creates awesome rogue-like dungeon levels. It is fully extensible and open source!  
  
If you end up using our library for anything please tell us about it! We would love to hear what you are working on...

### Authors and Contributors
William Blount @billylegota - Lead designer  
Seth Silva @sethdoescpp     - Co Programmer
